{"type":null,"faqId":44825,"title":"如何利用情景智能设置生日提醒？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.06875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4729167in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">可以通过情景智能功能实现。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">首先需开启情景智能中的生日提醒：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">下拉通知栏，点击“情景智能”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span class=\"s1\">打开“情景智能”，点击设置-事项类型，打开生日开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">然后在联系人界面创建生日记录：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161796\" style=\"width:2.4284723in;height:3.601389in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161797\" style=\"width:2.46875in;height:3.613889in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161798\" style=\"width:2.5104167in;height:2.7909722in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">在“联系人”界面，选择需要创建提醒的联系人，点击“编辑”进入编辑界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“添加其他项”&gt; “生日”，然后选择年月日信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击“完成”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">4.  </span><span class=\"s1\">点击屏幕右上方的“√”，完成保存。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161799\" style=\"width:2.6555555in;height:3.1895833in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161800\" style=\"width:2.667361in;height:3.5923612in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161801\" style=\"width:2.5625in;height:4.5208335in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161802\" style=\"width:2.5756946in;height:4.5194445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161803\" style=\"width:2.5840278in;height:4.1041665in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"326","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409267000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"情景智能,设置,生日提醒","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}